        <h3>Serge Osaulenko</h3>
        <p class="cred">Broker, Everlane Realty &middot; FL License #BK3384892</p>
        <p class="bio">I'm Serge Osaulenko, broker and owner of Everlane Realty in downtown St. Petersburg &mdash; licensed since 2017, running my own brokerage since 2020 (FL BK3384892).</p>
        <p class="bio">Before real estate I studied it &mdash; degrees in Real Estate and Finance from Florida State &mdash; then spent fourteen years building and selling a restaurant business. That's where I learned what a contract really is: the place deals quietly succeed or fail. Reading them closely is still my favorite part of the job.</p>
        <p class="bio">I work where I live &mdash; from the Pink Streets at Pinellas Point north through St. Pete and up the coast toward Clearwater. I speak English and Russian. Ask me the messy version of your situation; I'll make it clear.</p>
